     5→//! - jjx_chalk: Empty commit marking a steeplechase event (pace-level)
     6→//! - Heat-level commits: nominate, slate, rail, tally, draft, retire
     7→//!
     8→//! Commit format: `jjb:BRAND:IDENTITY[:ACTION]: message`
     9→//! - BRAND: Repository identifier (e.g., "RBM")
    10→//! - IDENTITY: ₢CORONET for pace-level, ₣FIREMARK for heat-level
    11→//! - ACTION: Single letter code (optional for standard notch)
